locality: Source of Namachidzi River, Nkhoma foothills, above Mbalambala Summit and Nkhoma Mission Dam
60 km from Iringa on Ruaha National Park Road. Acacia, Commiphora thicket.
Selous Game Reserve. T.8- Kingupira Forest.

K7, Lamu District: Witu Forest, N of road, forest at northern point of reserve and up to 1 km SE, bordering on swamp grassland with Combretum schumannii, Dialium orientale, Balanites wilsoniana, Craibia and Lonchocarpus.
Nampula: Nampula, arredores do Hospital Psiquiatricos, Etrada para Hospital de Mare.
